Package app.ini

Interface IIniConfig

All Known Implementing Classes:
CustomIIniConfig, Settings
public interface IIniConfig
Specifies all methods required by INI library.

      void putComment​(java.lang.String sectionName, java.lang.String comment)

      Parameters:
      sectionName - section name
      comment - comment to add

    • putComment

      void putComment​(java.lang.String sectionName, java.lang.String key, java.lang.String comment)
      Adds the comment to the specified item in the section.

      If the section is null, the comment is used as a header for the whole ini configuration. If the key is null, the comment is used as a header for the specified section. If both the section and the key are null, than the comment is used as the header for the whole ini configuration.

      Parameters:
      sectionName -
      key -
      comment -
